Comment: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}踊る1 2 3 steps on this dark stage
Comment: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Raise your flag, march on, fight
